    <section class="about" id="about">
        <div class="about-img">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555396273-367ea4eb4db5?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1374&q=80" loading="lazy" alt="Mone Rekho Restaurant">
        </div>
        <div class="about-content">
            <h2>Our Story</h2>
            <p>Founded in 2010, Mone Rekho has been serving authentic Kolkata-style fast food with love and passion. Our recipes have been passed down through generations, preserving the traditional flavors while adapting to modern tastes.</p>
            <p>We source only the freshest ingredients and prepare each dish with meticulous attention to detail. Our biryanis are cooked in the traditional dum style, ensuring every grain of rice is infused with flavor.</p>
            <p>At Mone Rekho, we believe food is not just about taste, but about creating memories that last a lifetime.</p>
